629
00:46:00,466 --> 00:46:02,009
The result wasn't surprising.

630
00:46:03,093 --> 00:46:04,219
Betrayal and scheme?

631
00:46:06,430 --> 00:46:08,265
Those are my expertise.

632
00:46:13,395 --> 00:46:14,563
