640
00:46:46,887 --> 00:46:48,514
I'm not sure,

641
00:46:49,890 --> 00:46:51,725
but one thing is certain.

642
00:46:53,727 --> 00:46:55,687
You worry about your candidate,

643
00:46:56,188 --> 00:46:58,815
